  "text": "Often, markdown optimization is the focus of these models. For example, [CITATION_1] examine the optimal control of prices during the liquidation of a fixed stock of product subject to price-dependent demand. See [CITATION_2] for an excellent review of the markdown optimization literature. Other works focus on inventory: [CITATION_3] study pre-season and replenishment inventory decisions when selling a seasonal good while [CITATION_4] examine assortment decisions at a fast-fashion retailer.",
